high_descs: turn around and walk to the couch, then turn left to face the coffee table in front of the couch
grab a remote control off of the table
move left a bit to face the table again
place the remote inside of the box on the table
pick up the box off of the table
move around to the other side of the table and face the other couch
place the box down on the couch cushions in front of you
anns.task_desc: place a box down on the couch with a remote in it

high_descs: Move to the coffee table.
Pick up the remote on the table next to the tissue box.
Bring the remote to the box on the table.
Put the remote in the box on the table.
Pick up the box on the table.
Bring the box on to the green couch.
Put the box on the green couch.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with remote in it on the green couch.

high_descs: Turn around, move towards the door, then turn left at the blue couch and move forward to the coffee table.
Pick up the remote control between the box of tissues and the credit card on the coffee table.
Turn left, move towards the shelves, then turn right and face cardboard box on the coffee table.
Place the remote control in the cardboard box on the coffee table.
Pick up the cardboard box containing the remote from the coffee table.
Move counterclockwise around the coffee table until you reach the middle of the couch next to the window then turn left and face the couch.
Place the cardboard box containing the remote on the left side of the couch near the window.
anns.task_desc: Place a cardboard box containing a remote on the couch.
